1 tbsp oil
1 Onion
Bacon
Garlic
1 tin tomatoes
200ml water
1 tbsp white wine vinegar (alternatively 100ml red wine, cook for 5 mins before adding tomatoes.)
3 Tsp sweet smoked paprika
45g parmesan
10g parmesan to top 
Optional chilli or 1/3 tsp crushed chillies.
Season to taste, salt depends on bacon.
Optional tsp sugar.

Serve with pasta or rice with cauliflower cooked in the sauce for 18min (the time it takes to cook the rice)
